OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776258665
OL,3,C'Likely' Noah Donohoe was alive when
OL,4,Che entered storm drain, inquest told
OL,6,FAn expert witness has told the inquest
OL,7,Finto Noah Donohoe's death that it is
OL,8,F"likely" that Noah was alive when he
OL,9,Fentered a storm drain in north
OL,10,FBelfast, where he was later found dead.
OL,12,FThe schoolboy was 14 when his naked
OL,13,Fbody was found in the storm drain
OL,14,Ftunnel on 27 June 2020.
OL,16,FHe had been missing for six days after
OL,17,Fleaving his home in south Belfast on
OL,18,Fhis bike to meet two friends in the
OL,19,FCavehill area of the city.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
