PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776258665
OL,3,C'Likely' Noah Donohoe was alive when
OL,4,Che entered storm drain, inquest told
OL,6,FA post-mortem examination found the
OL,7,Fcause of death was likely to be
OL,8,Fdrowning.
OL,10,FThe inquest into his death, which is
OL,11,Fbeing heard with a jury, resumed
OL,12,Ffollowing the Easter break on Monday.
OL,14,FThe proceedings at Belfast Coroner's
OL,15,FCourt heard a report by Professor
OL,16,FCarolyn Roberts, who had been
OL,17,Fcommissioned by the Coroner's Service,
OL,18,Fand had visited the site as well as
OL,19,Fconsidering "extensive material".
OL,26,@{D@MOU{D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
