OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776258665
OL,3,C'Likely' Noah Donohoe was alive when
OL,4,Che entered storm drain, inquest told
OL,6,FIn her report, which was read to the
OL,7,Finquest, she found that Noah was
OL,8,Flikely to have climbed through the
OL,9,Fbars into the storm drain before
OL,10,Fdrowning.
OL,12,F"The bars of the grille are
OL,13,Fsufficiently widely spaced that a
OL,14,Flarge child or even a small man could
OL,15,Fdeliberately climb through without
OL,16,Fundue effort," her report found.
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776258665
OL,3,C'Likely' Noah Donohoe was alive when
OL,4,Che entered storm drain, inquest told
OL,6,F"In my opinion, it is hence likely
OL,7,Fthat the boy climbed into (the)
OL,8,Fculvert entrance alive, slipping
OL,9,Fbetween the vertical metal bars of the
OL,10,Fmetal grille."
OL,12,FThe storm drain tunnel led under the
OL,13,FM2 motorway, train tracks and Seaview
OL,14,Fstadium to Belfast Lough.
OL,16,FProf Roberts found Noah was likely to
OL,17,Fhave walked while crouched in the
OL,18,Ftunnel, and with rising water levels
OL,19,Fand low light, may have become
OL,20,Fdisoriented.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776258665
OL,3,C'Likely' Noah Donohoe was alive when
OL,4,Che entered storm drain, inquest told
OL,6,F"The layout is relatively complex, and
OL,7,Ffor an unfamiliar person moving in
OL,8,Fsemi-darkness, in my opinion, it would
OL,9,Fappear possible to become disoriented.
OL,10,FThis is the section from which Noah's
OL,11,Fbody was recovered," her report went
OL,12,Fon.
OL,14,FHer report also found that high tide
OL,15,Fwas likely to have happened between
OL,16,F11.30pm and midnight on June 21 2020.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776258665
OL,3,C'Likely' Noah Donohoe was alive when
OL,4,Che entered storm drain, inquest told
OL,6,F"This is some five or six hours after
OL,7,Fhis (Noah's) last sighting, which
OL,8,Fwould allow ample time for him to have
OL,9,Fmade his way several hundred metres
OL,10,Falong the culvert," her report found.
OL,12,F"At this point, water is likely to
OL,13,Fhave risen almost completely to fill
OL,14,Fthe culvert around and immediately
OL,15,Fabove the point at which the boy's
OL,16,Fbody was discovered, creating
OL,17,Fconditions for drowning.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@SO]tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776258665
OL,3,C'Likely' Noah Donohoe was alive when
OL,4,Che entered storm drain, inquest told
OL,6,F"The quadrant would fill with water
OL,7,Frelatively quickly, and in darkness,
OL,8,Fwith a complex network of pipes and
OL,9,Fcold conditions, the boy would be
OL,10,Flikely to have become confused, in my
OL,11,Fopinion.
OL,13,F"It is possible that the boy survived
OL,14,Fin the culvert for several tidal
OL,15,Fcycles prior to succumbing. However,
OL,16,Fthe ground and air temperatures would
OL,17,Fnot be conducive to this with a naked
OL,18,Fbody, in my opinion."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
