PN,44608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776258665
OL,3,C'Likely' Noah Donohoe was alive when
OL,4,Che entered storm drain, inquest told
OL,6,FThe report went on: "Noah Donohoe is
OL,7,Flikely to have entered the Premier
OL,8,FDrive stream culvert behind Northwood
OL,9,FRoad in the late afternoon of June 21,
OL,10,F2020, by climbing through the metal
OL,11,Fgrille at the entrance, and crawling
OL,12,For walking in a stooped manner along
OL,13,Fthe culvert some 600 metres.
OL,15,F"This would have been in almost
OL,16,Fcomplete darkness... and would have
OL,17,Frequired some persistence, including
OL,18,Fclimbing under hanging obstacles.
OL,26,@nD@UOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
