OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776258665
OL,3,C'Likely' Noah Donohoe was alive when
OL,4,Che entered storm drain, inquest told
OL,6,FThe inquest also heard expert evidence
OL,7,Fwhich was critical of public safety
OL,8,Fwith regard to the culvert at Premier
OL,9,FDrive.
OL,11,FIn his report, which was read to the
OL,12,Finquest, Dr Mark Cooper said a risk
OL,13,Fassessment carried out by the
OL,14,FDepartment for Infrastructure, which
OL,15,Fowns the amenity, was "very
OL,16,Frudimentary" and focused on risks to
OL,17,FRivers Agency staff, rather than
OL,18,Fmembers of the public, noting a
OL,19,Fchildren's playground nearby.
OL,26,@wD@WOUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776258665
OL,3,C'Likely' Noah Donohoe was alive when
OL,4,Che entered storm drain, inquest told
OL,6,F"It is clear to me there was knowledge
OL,7,Fin the body corporate of the Rivers
OL,8,FAgency that the grille was in an area
OL,9,Fthat could attract members of the
OL,10,Fpublic and children," his report
OL,11,Fobserved.
OL,13,F"This does not look like it has had
OL,14,Fthe full care and attention that it
OL,15,Fought. I am critical in that the
OL,16,Fassessment does not consider who may
OL,17,Fbe harmed in considering hazards or
OL,18,Fexisting conditions."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@UO]uD@AOUzD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/12
